 arriv there at 7.30 Pm . I found my two chum at home in my Hut they had a nice fire go the hut was veri warm . After have a chat for a while , I went into anoth hut to see anoth Pall who was bad with Cramp , I made some Coffe put all the Rum I had left in it him I had a nice hot drink . After have a chat with him I went back to my hut , where my two chum were have Supper of Toast Cocoa , so I join them had a drop , one of the chap was on the Shunter at Midnight so I turn into his bed had a good sleep. The hut was veri warm all night , outsid it was freez . As my Train left Poperingh at 9.27 am , I got up at 7.30 am after have breakfast , I left the Camp at 8.15 am walk into The Town . As it was bitter cold I put on my Balaclava under my Big Hat , to keep my neck ear warm , the frost give my ear what Oh . I arriv in Town at 9 . am went into see my Lady-Friend to have a Cup of Coffe with her . I found her well had just came home from Church , she wonder what had becom of me as I had not seen her for a month . I am station to far away to get into town veri often . After say good bye I walk along to the Station where I produc my Movement
